Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.60,0:00:04.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0090,,{\fad(400,400)\fs36\fnMSungHK-Bold\bord0\shad2}2024年6月24日 第48層 林達斯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.54,0:00:14.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.35,0:00:18.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝啦 莉茲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.84,0:00:20.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝惠顧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.97,0:00:25.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天不參加公會的攻略嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.03,0:00:28.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我今天請假了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.08,0:00:31.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為跟人約好了今天見面
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.79,0:00:37.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.42,0:00:38.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.59,0:00:42.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我該走了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.23,0:00:48.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞絲娜找到重要的東西了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.13,0:00:50.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼來著
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.47,0:00:53.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.79,0:00:54.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要好好發展哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.36,0:00:56.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 不是那回事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.23,0:00:58.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那再見了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.82,0:01:10.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也會找到嗎

Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.34,0:01:28.70,OP1JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}認めてた臆病な過去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.06,0:01:36.77,OP1JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}分からないままに怖がってた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.14,0:01:38.89,OP1JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}後ろの自分が
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.97,0:01:45.72,OP1JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}現実を今に映す
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.83,0:01:50.83,OP1JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}いくつもの空を描いた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.20,0:01:52.89,OP1JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}ここはきっと
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.20,0:01:58.37,OP1JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}儚い心 乱して
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.59,0:02:04.08,OP1JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}夢で高く飛んだ躰は
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.15,0:02:06.94,OP1JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}どんな不安纏っても
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.10,0:02:08.98,OP1JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}振り払ってく
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.31,0:02:13.42,OP1JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}眠る小さな想い
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.67,0:02:15.64,OP1JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}広がりだして
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.82,0:02:17.70,OP1JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}気づく 弱い 私
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.84,0:02:24.40,OP1JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}君がいれば 暗い世界 強くいれた
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.25,0:02:30.16,OP1JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}長い夢見る心は そう 永遠で
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.77,0:02:34.27,OP1JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}I wanna always stay with you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.45,0:02:39.87,OP1JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}I give you everything I have

Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.34,0:01:28.70,OP1CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}正視著膽怯的過去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.06,0:01:36.77,OP1CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}依然無法理解地畏懼著
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.14,0:01:38.89,OP1CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}背後的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.97,0:01:45.72,OP1CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}此刻映照在現實中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.83,0:01:50.83,OP1CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}描繪了數片天空的此處
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.20,0:01:52.89,OP1CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}一定是在
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.20,0:01:58.37,OP1CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}亂我脆弱心扉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.59,0:02:04.08,OP1CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}乘著夢想高飛身軀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.15,0:02:06.94,OP1CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}無論有任何不安糾纏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.10,0:02:08.98,OP1CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}都掙脫前進
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.31,0:02:13.42,OP1CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}將沉睡著的小小的心願
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.67,0:02:15.64,OP1CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}擴展開來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.82,0:02:17.70,OP1CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}意識到弱小的我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.84,0:02:24.40,OP1CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}只要有你在 黑暗的世界 也能一直堅強
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.25,0:02:30.16,OP1CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}用沉眠許久的心 永遠堅強
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.77,0:02:34.27,OP1CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}I wanna always stay with you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.45,0:02:39.87,OP1CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur1}I give you everything I have

