Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.98,0:02:57.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心的溫度
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.96,0:03:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,強差人意
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.99,0:03:15.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接客也是工作的一環
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.39,0:03:19.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.32,0:03:25.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎來到莉茲貝特武器店
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.84,0:03:31.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那個 我想訂做武器
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.29,0:03:38.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他付得起錢嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.51,0:03:42.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前金屬的市價略有上漲…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.27,0:03:44.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,預算方面你不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.46,0:03:47.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想你打造出目前所能打造的最好的劍
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.71,0:03:49.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然你這麼說…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.74,0:03:53.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你不具體給出性能的目標值的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.28,0:03:54.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 說的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.42,0:03:59.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那要求性能不低於這把劍如何
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.57,0:04:04.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闡釋者
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.48,0:04:09.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在怪物掉落的武器中好比是魔劍級別的怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.25,0:04:11.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能做出來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.07,0:04:16.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這把如何
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.80,0:04:19.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我所鍛造的最高傑作
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.46,0:04:23.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有點輕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.82,0:04:26.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為使用的是速度系的金屬
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.25,0:04:28.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以測試一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.10,0:04:30.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,測試什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.54,0:04:31.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它的耐久度
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.92,0:04:37.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢著 要是那麼做你的劍會斷的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.64,0:04:39.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到時斷了再說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.64,0:04:55.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修復…不可
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.76,0:05:07.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你搞什麼啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.16,0:05:11.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我沒想到會是作出斬擊的那把斷了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.93,0:05:15.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的意思是我的劍比預料中要不堪一擊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.98,0:05:18.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.62,0:05:22.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話先說在前頭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.32,0:05:23.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是有材料
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.77,0:05:26.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能輕易砍斷你那把劍的武器
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.42,0:05:28.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要多少我都能鍛造出來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.19,0:05:30.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呵呵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.32,0:05:34.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那務必請你做出一把能輕易砍斷這把劍的來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.00,0:05:38.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然說到了這個份上 你就給我奉陪到底
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.61,0:05:39.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奉陪到底?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.59,0:05:41.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 首先陪我去採集金屬
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.75,0:05:44.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一個人去就足夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.54,0:05:46.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不想被你拖累
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.91,0:05:48.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要小看我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.54,0:05:51.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好歹也是個熟練的戰錘使
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.04,0:05:54.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要找的金屬在哪?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.80,0:05:56.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在第55層的西山上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.97,0:05:59.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎有一條以水晶為食的龍
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.85,0:06:03.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傳聞在它體內囤積著大量稀有金屬
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.43,0:06:05.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第55層啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.45,0:06:06.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.35,0:06:08.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要想得到金屬
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.18,0:06:10.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貌似必須要有冶煉師同行哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.85,0:06:12.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便如此你還是想一個人去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.55,0:06:22.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要乖乖地躲在我背後
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.77,0:06:24.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.09,0:06:25.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫桐人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.77,0:06:28.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在劍造好之前請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.39,0:06:29.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多指教 桐人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.88,0:06:32.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一下子就直呼其名啊 不過算了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.30,0:06:34.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉茲貝特
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.96,0:06:47.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0090,,{\fad(400,0)\fs36\fnMSungHK-Bold\bord0\shad2}第55層 西山
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.01,0:06:47.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.83,0:06:49.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒衣可添了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.04,0:06:53.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒想到55層會是冰天雪地
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.21,0:06:59.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不冷嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.35,0:07:02.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我鍛煉的方式跟你不同
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.10,0:07:05.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是盡讓人惱火
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.57,0:07:08.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好暖和
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.54,0:07:13.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我居然會和這種男人單獨出門
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.29,0:07:16.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不可思議的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.60,0:07:17.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 莉茲貝特
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.31,0:07:19.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經走不動了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.88,0:07:21.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還遊刃有餘呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.35,0:07:24.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說 終歸要直呼名字的話叫我莉茲就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.74,0:07:26.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好 我明白了 莉茲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.04,0:07:28.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別得意忘形
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.33,0:07:42.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好美
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.27,0:07:47.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.13,0:07:50.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備好轉移水晶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.99,0:07:52.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.61,0:07:54.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有 之後就由我一個人來應付
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.28,0:07:59.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等龍出現之後 莉茲就躲到那邊的水晶後面
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.41,0:08:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千萬不要出來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.00,0:08:01.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.15,0:08:04.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又不是外行 當然要幫忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.50,0:08:05.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.15,0:08:12.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.77,0:08:14.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.74,0:08:26.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,躲到那後面去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.15,0:08:27.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.89,0:08:43.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呼息攻擊 快躲開
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.18,0:08:52.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.21,0:08:54.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僅憑那麼纖細的武器就…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.20,0:08:56.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他究竟是何方神聖
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.62,0:09:09.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 趕緊收拾掉它吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.11,0:09:10.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 先別出來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.27,0:09:15.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛 不是已經結束了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.05,0:09:20.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉茲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.05,0:09:33.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉茲 抓緊了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.42,0:09:51.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還活著嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.28,0:09:56.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.23,0:10:00.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姑且先把它喝了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.38,0:10:02.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.98,0:10:16.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…謝謝你來救我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.82,0:10:19.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要道謝還太早了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.25,0:10:21.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先想想怎麼上去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.21,0:10:23.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用傳送不就行了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.32,0:10:27.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傳送 林達斯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.24,0:10:30.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.60,0:10:34.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用不了水晶就說明應該還有別的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.75,0:10:36.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不知道是否真的如此
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.68,0:10:40.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這還可能是被設計為掉下去的人百分百會死的陷阱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.62,0:10:42.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此 你說的也有道理
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.32,0:10:45.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.33,0:10:47.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道就不能多說點振奮人心的話來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.29,0:10:48.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有一個主意
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.83,0:10:49.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.27,0:10:50.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.45,0:10:53.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沿著牆壁跑上去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.20,0:10:57.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是笨蛋嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.01,0:11:00.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是否笨蛋試過就知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.94,0:11:06.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.15,0:11:20.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,助跑距離能再長一點的話就能跑上去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.87,0:11:22.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不可能呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.32,0:11:30.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺好奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.48,0:11:32.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現實中根本不可能發生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.61,0:11:37.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這個初次踏足的地方和初次認識的人並排著睡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.64,0:11:40.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且這人還想往牆上跑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.37,0:11:43.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個奇怪的傢伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.51,0:11:44.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.51,0:11:53.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說桐人 能問你一個問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.33,0:11:54.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 一副鄭重其事的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.03,0:11:58.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼那個時候你要來救我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.45,0:12:02.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與其對別人見死不救
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.51,0:12:05.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是大家死在一塊更好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.53,0:12:09.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更不要說是像莉茲這樣的女孩子了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.83,0:12:12.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是個笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.91,0:12:14.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有誰會像你這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.83,0:12:20.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.43,0:12:22.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,握著我的手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.46,0:12:30.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.12,0:12:40.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好溫暖
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.99,0:12:46.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和桐人明明都只是虛擬世界的數據而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.68,0:12:48.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉茲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.17,0:13:05.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.08,0:13:16.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.13,0:13:18.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.98,0:13:27.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs36\fnMSungHK-Bold}水晶石英鑄塊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.13,0:13:23.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個難不成是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.96,0:13:27.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 應該就是我們要來找的金屬了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.03,0:13:31.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍吃下水晶 在腹中生成金屬
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.65,0:13:35.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難怪找不到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.54,0:13:36.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.28,0:13:39.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是為什麼會在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.40,0:13:43.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個深坑不是陷阱 而是龍的巢穴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.39,0:13:48.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說那鑄塊是龍的排泄物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.41,0:13:49.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是糞便
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.24,0:13:57.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎樣 目標總算是達成了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.87,0:13:58.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.35,0:14:04.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說過這裡是龍的巢穴對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.15,0:14:04.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.02,0:14:09.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記得龍好像是夜行性的 也就是說現在差不多要…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.07,0:14:15.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.95,0:14:21.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…等…幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.53,0:14:33.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉茲 抓緊了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.52,0:14:43.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到外面了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.45,0:14:59.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好壯觀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.99,0:15:11.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桐人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.03,0:15:13.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.61,0:15:14.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.64,0:15:19.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡桐人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.36,0:15:23.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼 我聽不見
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.71,0:15:26.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.16,0:15:40.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0090,,{\fad(400,400)\fs36\fnMSungHK-Bold\bord0\shad2}2024年6月25日 第48層 林達斯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.42,0:15:39.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是要單手用的長劍對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.76,0:15:41.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.33,0:15:56.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桐人手心的溫暖
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.53,0:15:57.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.14,0:15:59.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都不是錯覺
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.02,0:16:05.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能打造出滿意的劍 我就表白我的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.14,0:16:26.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名字是「逐暗者」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.64,0:16:28.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是第一次聽說這名字
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.26,0:16:30.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說明這把劍應該沒有被收錄到請報商的武器名冊裡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.86,0:16:32.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,試試看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.24,0:16:42.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.17,0:16:43.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好重啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.64,0:16:44.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是把好劍
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.13,0:16:45.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.52,0:16:48.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劍裡面彷彿蘊藏著靈魂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.76,0:16:58.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 這樣一來委託就算完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.88,0:17:00.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該付你造劍的價款了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.37,0:17:00.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要多少錢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.44,0:17:03.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那個
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.91,0:17:07.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不收你錢了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.51,0:17:09.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與之交換
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.04,0:17:14.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望桐人能讓我當你的專屬鍛造師
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.81,0:17:17.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼意思…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.34,0:17:21.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉茲?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.87,0:17:28.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從野外回來後就來這裡讓我給你保養裝備
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.21,0:17:28.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天都要
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.13,0:17:30.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今後一直如此
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.14,0:17:34.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉茲…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.48,0:17:39.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桐人 我…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.60,0:17:42.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉茲 我好擔心你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.92,0:17:44.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞…亞絲娜?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.73,0:17:45.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉茲!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.94,0:17:47.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發不到信息給你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.30,0:17:48.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又無法用地圖追蹤到你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.87,0:17:50.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚你到底去哪了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.66,0:17:54.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 昨天我稍微在迷宮裡滯留了一晚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.28,0:17:55.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迷宮?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.40,0:17:56.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉茲一個人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.81,0:17:58.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我是跟這個人一起的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.04,0:18:01.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桐…桐人?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.25,0:18:04.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲 亞絲娜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.55,0:18:06.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久…也算不上好久
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.76,0:18:07.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩天不見了?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.17,0:18:09.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真嚇我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.67,0:18:11.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊 原來你這麼快就來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.72,0:18:14.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我說一聲的話 我也會一起來的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.34,0:18:16.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩位難道是認識的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.78,0:18:19.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我們兩個都是攻略組的人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.45,0:18:23.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為他說想要把強力的劍
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.88,0:18:25.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就把莉茲的店介紹給他了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.78,0:18:27.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.42,0:18:30.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒對我的摯友做出什麼奇怪的舉動吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.30,0:18:32.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.06,0:18:34.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吞吞吐吐的好可疑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.76,0:18:36.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我剛剛才死裡逃生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.30,0:18:38.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微體恤一下我也不為過吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.41,0:18:42.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才反覆叫你儘量不要單獨行動
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.79,0:18:45.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊 原來是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.88,0:18:49.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這人有沒有對莉茲出言冒犯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.99,0:18:52.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉茲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.50,0:18:57.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何止是出言冒犯的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.92,0:19:01.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙直接把我店裡最好的劍給一下子砍斷了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.55,0:19:03.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗚哇 抱歉…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.86,0:19:06.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞絲娜沒有必要道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.94,0:19:10.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 雖然是個怪人但也不是壞人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.96,0:19:12.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會支持你的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.35,0:19:13.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油啊 亞絲娜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.60,0:19:16.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說不是那回事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.35,0:19:18.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉茲?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.36,0:19:20.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我跟人約好了去進貨
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.82,0:19:21.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要出去一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.64,0:19:24.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那店舖怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.35,0:19:26.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有勞二位幫忙看店
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.63,0:19:29.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 莉茲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.56,0:19:48.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉茲貝特
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.20,0:19:57.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼可以現在就來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.11,0:20:01.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明再過一會兒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.16,0:20:05.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就能變回往常那個朝氣蓬勃的莉茲貝特
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.48,0:20:06.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉茲…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.94,0:20:09.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為什麼會知道我在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.36,0:20:17.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是從那裡眺望整個城鎮才找到的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.18,0:20:20.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是那麼亂來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.55,0:20:29.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我已經沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.10,0:20:33.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是被不習慣的冒險給嚇到了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.86,0:20:37.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…剛才我說的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.16,0:20:40.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請全都忘記吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.86,0:20:45.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我想跟莉茲道謝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.09,0:20:47.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直以來…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.72,0:20:54.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直以來我都覺得與其一個人苟活不如死個痛快
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.67,0:20:56.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的是這麼想的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.78,0:20:58.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桐人…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.36,0:21:01.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 掉進洞穴的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.62,0:21:04.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們一起共度的時光真的很愉快
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.85,0:21:09.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也認識到了所有人都是為了生存而生存的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.82,0:21:13.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 謝謝你 莉茲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.43,0:21:17.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.59,0:21:21.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在尋找著切實存在於這個世界裡的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.44,0:21:24.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而對我來說
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.86,0:21:28.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桐人掌心的溫暖就是我所尋求的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.44,0:21:34.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我剛才的話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.99,0:21:36.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也讓亞絲娜聽聽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.23,0:21:37.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉茲…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.33,0:21:39.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.84,0:21:43.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這份溫暖還會殘留一段時間
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.99,0:21:47.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.73,0:21:51.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由桐人來終結這個世界吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.38,0:21:55.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此之前我會努力不懈的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.94,0:21:58.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我向你保證
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.86,0:22:00.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定會把這個遊戲通關
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.44,0:22:07.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要修理武器和防具的話可以隨時來找我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.53,0:22:12.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今後也請多多光臨莉茲貝特武器店

Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.12,0:22:39.25,ED1JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}遠くに聞こえた鐘の音が少し寂しくて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.99,0:22:51.29,ED1JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}もう一度強く 今度は高く駆け抜けた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.81,0:23:02.96,ED1JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}ただ繰り返す現実も 星の数の願い事も
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.67,0:23:13.89,ED1JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}目指すべき明日を見つけた この想いには勝てない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.22,0:23:24.78,ED1JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}目の前に開かれた果てない世界 たとえ仮想でもいい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.16,0:23:37.58,ED1JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}迷い続けても 胸の奥で強くずっとずっと響いてく
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.02,0:23:44.11,ED1JP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}そっと そっと 光ってる

Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.12,0:22:39.25,ED1CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}從遠處傳來的鐘聲略帶寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.99,0:22:51.29,ED1CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}再度強有力地疾馳而過 比上次躍得更高
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.81,0:23:02.96,ED1CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}只是日復一日地虛度光陰 在此許下多如繁星的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.67,0:23:13.89,ED1CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}皆不如明確未來目標的這份決意
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.22,0:23:24.78,ED1CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}展開在眼前的無垠世界 就算只是場虛構的夢也沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.16,0:23:37.58,ED1CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}就算迷惘依舊 內心深處那強而有力的聲響也永不停息
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.02,0:23:44.11,ED1CH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}靜靜地閃耀著光輝

Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.25,0:23:49.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回 黑白交錯的劍之舞